    "We wish to frame briefly our section on MPC: although it would not be considered a classic case of ML, we find it helpful to thoroughly embed the motivations behind its development and active use into our understanding of the learning-based methods to follow.",
    "Thus, we will spend significant time describing it.",
    "The key idea of MPC is to predict the value of the objective function in the future using an auxiliary dynamical model of the building's behavior and to select a control action that optimizes the predicted reward.",
    "Generally, if the dynamics model is f, the action u, the state x, the objective y, and the current timestep t, then MPC solves:",
